    <stitle>10 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS FULLER RT-610 SERIES - REMOVE - AIR VALVE</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="IDcomponent" graphiccount="2">
        <title>AIR VALVE</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the two air lines between the air valve and the air cylinder in the auxiliary.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the four bolts and the air valve from the transmission (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302410">Figure 10</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f1302410" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302410" filename="../figg13/G1302410.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 10. Remove Air Valve</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">If necessary, remove the fittings from the air valve.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the actuating spring and pin from the bore in the transmission (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302411">Figure 11</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f1302411" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302411" filename="../figg13/G1302411.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 11. Remove Actuating Spring and Pin</caption>
        </figure>
    </svcproc>
